{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_53_03",
  "title": "kana",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――四月十日　夜",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1266.6666667,
          "startTime": 1.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ふ～、ようやくkanaさんのお誕生日プレゼントが\n購入出来ましたわ。これならkanaさんも大喜び――",
      "startTime": 7.1333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5900.0000635999995,
          "startTime": 13.0333333969
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 12.7999997257
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "お、すずじゃん、また会ったね～。こんな時間に\n何してんの？　お子ちゃまは補導されんぞ",
      "startTime": 17.2333333969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 21.0666665195
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "かかかかかkanaさん！？　まだ補導される時間では\nありませんわ！　kanaさんこそ何してるんですの！",
      "startTime": 24.833333524,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8533.333206200003,
          "startTime": 33.3666667302
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 26.6000001907
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 29.366665248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "仕事が早めに終わったから買い物してたの～\nkana、今日お誕生日だし～？",
      "startTime": 32.9000000636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 35.4999985813
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そ、その手に持っている紙袋は？",
      "startTime": 35.4999985813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 40.1333316604
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "いつも使ってるブランドの新作美容液！\nちょっと高めなんだけど気になってたんだよね～",
      "startTime": 43.9000000636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 47.2999998529
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "（ヤバいですわ、ヤバいですわ、ヤバいですわぁぁ！）\n（完全に私が用意したプレゼントと同じ美容液……！）",
      "startTime": 51.6847845514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 56.5666665196
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "あー、そう言えばまだすずちゃんからプレゼント\nもらってなかったな～。何くれるのか楽しみだなぁ～",
      "startTime": 60.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 65.6000023961
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "成宮家のご令嬢なんだし、さぞ豪華で高価な物を\nくれるんだろうな～。もちろん万バズ確定の一品を！",
      "startTime": 70.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 75.4666716058
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "ひぃ……っ！　期待して下さってるのは嬉しいのですが\n『バズる物』というのは非常に難しく……",
      "startTime": 81.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 86.4333397984
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 90.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "あはははっ、冗談に決まってんでしょ。山田さんじゃ\nないんだし、中学生にたかったりしないから、安心しな",
      "startTime": 91.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 95.7666731317
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "いえ！　私成宮すずは、この難関ミッションをクリアし\n必ずや人間として一回りも二回りも大きくなるのですわ",
      "startTime": 101.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14099.999999999995,
          "startTime": 115.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 107.76667008
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 112.4333367466
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "こうなったら……渡すしかないですわ！　kanaさん\n私からのプレゼントを受け取ってくださいまし～～！",
      "startTime": 113.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6866.666666699999,
          "startTime": 120.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 119.6666670282
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、あんた、こんな所でそんなにデカい声出したら\n見つか……わわわ、ほらどんどん人が集まって来た！",
      "startTime": 122.6999969482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 123.6399969482
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-night",
      "startTime": 129.050003922
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-night",
      "startTime": 129.050003922
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "ファンの対応に時間取られたせいでもうこんな時間……\nまだ買い物したかったのに。おい、人の話聞いてる？",
      "startTime": 134.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-night",
      "startTime": 137.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-night",
      "startTime": 140.3333331864
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "ふふんっ、もちろん聞いてますわ！　ですが！\nSNSのトレンドを見て下さいまし、大バズリですわ！",
      "startTime": 145.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-night",
      "startTime": 151.2333352209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "私達が皆さんにファンサしている写真や動画が撮られて\n沢山SNSに投稿されているんですの！",
      "startTime": 156.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-night",
      "startTime": 159.9333138586
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "「kanaちゃんに直接おめでとうを言えるなんて」\n「kanaちゃん、リアル天使。神対応過ぎ」",
      "startTime": 163.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-night",
      "startTime": 167.3333138586
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "トレンドも一位が「kana誕生祭」\n二位が「kanaすず出没」！　さすが私達ですわね！",
      "startTime": 170.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-night",
      "startTime": 174.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-night",
      "startTime": 176.8333138586
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、ファンのみんなから直接おめでとうって言って\nもらえたのは嬉しいけどさー。これがプレゼント？",
      "startTime": 180.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 13366.666666599996,
          "startTime": 193.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-night",
      "startTime": 185.2333057206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "ち、違いますわ！　プレゼントはしっかりと\n用意してますわよ……！　ですが……こちらです",
      "startTime": 189.2666585286,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7033.341471400007,
          "startTime": 196.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-night",
      "startTime": 193.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-night",
      "startTime": 195.7333138586
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_03-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "これは……kanaがさっき買ったのと同じ美容液！\nめっちゃ嬉しい！　高かったでしょ？　本当にいいの？",
      "startTime": 201.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
